,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"台灣唔承認雙重國籍（香港人），用完特區再轉BNO有機會入唔到境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcaaf62c4f8327801a14f129556fafa7276c6a2","tid":1622231,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467138c155daa728dda2aaf9c70426c0b001ec05","tid":1622231,"uid":123706,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"台灣唔承認雙重國籍（香港人），用完特區再轉BNO有機會入唔到境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"臺灣旅行英國國民（海外）護照及特區護照問題<br />\n<br />\n中華民國<br />\n<br />\n香港澳門關係條例<br />\n<br />\n第四條 本條例所稱香港居民，指具有香港永久居留資格，且未持有英國國民（海外）護照或香港護照以外之旅行證照者。<br />\n<br />\n本條例所稱澳門居民，指具有澳門永久居留資格，且未持有澳門護照以外之旅行證照或雖持有葡萄牙護照但係於葡萄牙結束治理前於澳門取得者。<br />\n<br />\n前二項香港或澳門居民，如於香港或澳門分別於英國及葡萄牙結束其治理前，取得華僑身分者及其符合中華民國國籍取得要件之配偶及子女，在本條例施行前之既有權益，應予以維護。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mac.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=24F1371BF3738F96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mac.gov.tw%2Fcp.aspx%3Fn%3D24F1371BF3738F96&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=d00c889d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mac.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=24F1371BF3738F96</a><br />\n<br />\n入臺證需要有中文姓名，因為入臺證根據閣下的香港永久居留資格而簽發，所以入臺證要以香港永久居民身份證上記載的資料輸入。否則臺灣入境當局可能會要求當場辦理入臺證 ( 300台幣 ) 。"},{"pid":"9ff8f7eb138b80fa2bb5d53c21e006206df6f268","tid":1622231,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"香港係撚國藉"},{"pid":"54a59f04da65e5eef2246cfc995aaee32b8878ae","tid":1622231,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:35:06.000Z","msg":"無問題"},{"pid":"fbfe31106eb2c4cad77b78a6da2123e64f104a0f","tid":1622231,"uid":57968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"入台證只需重新申請就得<br />\n填新 passport number"},{"pid":"02f3140e4455973d57b77b47eedbef5aad32fc82","tid":1622231,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecdef3f0d515da9a6b2396c52ae9471a4517f2ea","tid":1622231,"uid":67779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73032514ffd6b2b1241551ddcafd425b82ffaa95","tid":1622231,"uid":136766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"我10月尾去福岡都等緊破處BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5acb3e3c4572883ffcf85e34a92c65d0d815ebc","tid":1622231,"uid":159128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecdef3f0d515da9a6b2396c52ae9471a4517f2ea","tid":1622231,"uid":67779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73032514ffd6b2b1241551ddcafd425b82ffaa95","tid":1622231,"uid":136766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"我10月尾去福岡都等緊破處BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:48:07.000Z